# GitHub Pages deploy verification

Production and preview use **legacy GitHub Pages** builds that take **1–6 minutes** after `git push`. The live URL may still serve the old `APP_VERSION` while `status=building`.

## After every push to `origin/main` and/or `preview`

Run and **do not tell the user deploy is complete** until this passes:

```bash
npm run deploy:verify
```

Or full push + verify from `dev`:

```bash
npm run deploy
```

## URLs

- Production: https://bnarcum.github.io/cisco-portfolio-navigator/cisco-portfolio-navigator.html
- Preview: https://bnarcum.github.io/cisco-portfolio-navigator-preview/cisco-portfolio-navigator.html

## If verification times out

Report the timeout, last live version seen, and link to repo Pages settings. Suggest hard refresh (Cmd+Shift+R). Do not claim the fix is live until `deploy:verify` succeeds.
